        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white ">
            <h5 class="text-left" style="font-size:21px;">Process</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">



            <ol style="font-size:18px;">
                For registration of Firm require minimum Entity Proof for open a Current Bank Account.
                We have the following option to take entity proof:
                <li>Application for name approval.</li>
                <li>Obtain Digital Signature Certificate.</li>
                <li>Drafting of MOA / AOA, other documents.</li>
                <li>Preparation of INC-9, DIR-2, Affidavit and other documents.<li>

                <li>Incorporation documents will be filed on MCA Portal</li>
                <li>Get Certificate of Incorporation</li>
            </ol>
        </div>





        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
            <h5 class="text-left" style="font-size:21px;"> Required Documents</h5>
        </div>

        <ol style="font-size:18px;">
            <li>Passport size color photograph of each subscribers</li>
            <li>Copy of PAN card (Passport in case of NRI) of each subscriber.</li>
            <li>Copy of address proof of each subscriber ( Bank Statement, telephone bill, electricity bill, mobile bill not older 2 months)</li>
            <li>Self attested copy of identity proof of each subscriber (Voters ID, Passport, Driving License, Adhar card)</li>
            <li>Address proof for Registered Office of the Company.(any utility bill, rent agreement, NOC from owner)</li>
            <li>Digital Signature Certificate (DSC) </li>
            <li>Main object of Company </li>
        </ol>

        
    </div>
</div>
